## Status Marker Legend

These markers are protocol values used by Harness tooling. Keep them unchanged
unless the project has tested parser aliases.

| Marker | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| `pm:дҫқй јдёӯ` | PM requested work |
| `cc:TODO` | Not started by Claude Code |
| `cc:WIP` | Claude Code is working |
| `cc:е®ҢдәҶ` | Claude Code completed the task and is awaiting confirmation |
| `pm:зўәиӘҚжёҲ` | PM confirmed completion |
| `cursor:дҫқй јдёӯ` | Compatibility alias for `pm:дҫқй јдёӯ` |
| `cursor:зўәиӘҚжёҲ` | Compatibility alias for `pm:зўәиӘҚжёҲ` |
| `blocked` | Blocked; include the reason next to the task |

